  "description": "<p>针对苹果的“Find My Phone”功能，索尼也开始加强这方面的服务，<a href=\"http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/224830.htm\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">在二月份开始陆续</a>在部分国家开展名为“My Xperia”服务，通过GPS信号来定位你手机当前的位置，甚至可以进行远程擦除和锁定设备的操作。<strong>而今天索尼正式宣告这项服务已经脱离了“beta” 头衔，目前已经为全球的索尼Xperia用户提供找回手机功能.</strong><br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e3bdb12/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243631.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E2%80%9CMy+Xperia%E2%80%9D%E8%84%B1%E7%A6%BBBeta%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC+%E4%B8%BA%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%89%BE%E5%9B%9E%E4%B8%A2%E5%A4%B1%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243631.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E2%80%9CMy+Xperia%E2%80%9D%E8%84%B1%E7%A6%BBBeta%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC+%E4%B8%BA%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%89%BE%E5%9B%9E%E4%B8%A2%E5%A4%B1%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243631.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E2%80%9CMy+Xperia%E2%80%9D%E8%84%B1%E7%A6%BBBeta%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC+%E4%B8%BA%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%89%BE%E5%9B%9E%E4%B8%A2%E5%A4%B1%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243631.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E2%80%9CMy+Xperia%E2%80%9D%E8%84%B1%E7%A6%BBBeta%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC+%E4%B8%BA%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E6%89%BE%E5%9B%9E%E4%B8%A2%E5%A4%B1%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"