  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/243630.htm", 
  "description": "<p>吉姆·霍洛克（Jim Hollock）的第一部书讲述的是发生在宾夕法尼亚州的真实犯罪故事。当这部书在2011年发行上市之后，评价非常积极，且销量也很得体。如今，《生下来就是失败》（Born to Lose）的销量已经开始下滑--而亚马逊却落井下石，把这部图书的售价上调了近三分之一。<strong>很多作家曾质问亚马逊为何自己的图书售价被上调，但亚马逊并未就此给出实质性的答复。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e3bdb11/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243630.htm&amp;t=%E4%BA%9A%E9%A9%AC%E9%80%8A%E6%82%84%E7%84%B6%E4%B8%8A%E8%B0%83%E5%9B%BE%E4%B9%A6%E5%94%AE%E4%BB%B7+%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E7%8B%AC%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%BC%E5%B1%80%E7%BB%88%E6%9D%A5%E4%B8%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243630.htm&amp;t=%E4%BA%9A%E9%A9%AC%E9%80%8A%E6%82%84%E7%84%B6%E4%B8%8A%E8%B0%83%E5%9B%BE%E4%B9%A6%E5%94%AE%E4%BB%B7+%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E7%8B%AC%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%BC%E5%B1%80%E7%BB%88%E6%9D%A5%E4%B8%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243630.htm&amp;t=%E4%BA%9A%E9%A9%AC%E9%80%8A%E6%82%84%E7%84%B6%E4%B8%8A%E8%B0%83%E5%9B%BE%E4%B9%A6%E5%94%AE%E4%BB%B7+%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E7%8B%AC%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%BC%E5%B1%80%E7%BB%88%E6%9D%A5%E4%B8%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243630.htm&amp;t=%E4%BA%9A%E9%A9%AC%E9%80%8A%E6%82%84%E7%84%B6%E4%B8%8A%E8%B0%83%E5%9B%BE%E4%B9%A6%E5%94%AE%E4%BB%B7+%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E7%8B%AC%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%BC%E5%B1%80%E7%BB%88%E6%9D%A5%E4%B8%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplu