  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/243629.htm", 
  "description": "<p><strong>美国洛杉矶时报网今天发表文章称，高昂的关税使得iPhone在巴西定价过高，导致苹果公司在巴西智能手机市场的份额不足10%，远落后于三星 40%多的份额。</strong>文章还指出，巴西只是苹果公司在全球新兴市场尴尬现状的一个缩影。为了实现持续增长，苹果公司在新兴市场的战略或需从根本上实现转变。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e3bdb10/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243629.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%8A%98%E6%88%9F%E6%96%B0%E5%85%B4%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%9A%E8%BF%9B%E5%B1%95%E7%BC%93%E6%85%A2%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%8E%8B%E5%88%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243629.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%8A%98%E6%88%9F%E6%96%B0%E5%85%B4%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%9A%E8%BF%9B%E5%B1%95%E7%BC%93%E6%85%A2%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%8E%8B%E5%88%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243629.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%8A%98%E6%88%9F%E6%96%B0%E5%85%B4%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%9A%E8%BF%9B%E5%B1%95%E7%BC%93%E6%85%A2%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%8E%8B%E5%88%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243629.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%8A%98%E6%88%9F%E6%96%B0%E5%85%B4%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%9A%E8%BF%9B%E5%B1%95%E7%BC%93%E6%85%A2%E8%A2%AB%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%8E%8B%E5%88%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.fee