  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/243628.htm", 
  "description": "<p>英国有着漫长的海岸线，也是世界上海洋风最活跃的地方，不过这也让它成为了可利用海洋风力发电资源的大国。<strong>本周，该国宣布了世界上最大的海上风电场——\"伦敦阵列\"(the London Array)——的开幕，其装机数为175台，总发电量更是达到了惊人的630兆瓦，远超世界上其它国家！</strong>英国当前有12%的电力来自可再生能源，但它希望到2020年的时候增加至30%。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e3bdb0e/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243628.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E9%A3%8E%E7%94%B5%E5%9C%BA+%22%E4%BC%A6%E6%95%A6%E9%98%B5%E5%88%97%22%E6%80%BB%E8%A3%85%E6%9C%BA%E9%87%8F630%E5%85%86%E7%93%A6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243628.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E9%A3%8E%E7%94%B5%E5%9C%BA+%22%E4%BC%A6%E6%95%A6%E9%98%B5%E5%88%97%22%E6%80%BB%E8%A3%85%E6%9C%BA%E9%87%8F630%E5%85%86%E7%93%A6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243628.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E9%A3%8E%E7%94%B5%E5%9C%BA+%22%E4%BC%A6%E6%95%A6%E9%98%B5%E5%88%97%22%E6%80%BB%E8%A3%85%E6%9C%BA%E9%87%8F630%E5%85%86%E7%93%A6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243628.htm&amp;t=%5B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E8%8B%B1%E5%9B%BD%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E9%A3%8E%E7%94%B5%E5%9C%BA+%22%E4%BC%A6%E6